{"ja485:0.1":"Jataka ","ja485:0.2":"Pakinnakanipata ","ja485:0.3":"Salikedaravagga ","ja485:0.4":"2. Candakinnarijataka ","ja485:1.1":"“Upaniyatidam manne, ","ja485:1.2":"cande lohitamaddane; ","ja485:1.3":"Ajja jahami jivitam, ","ja485:1.4":"pana me cande nirujjhanti. ","ja485:2.1":"Osidi me dukkham hadayam, ","ja485:2.2":"Me dayhate nitammami; ","ja485:2.3":"Tava candiya socantiya, ","ja485:2.4":"Na nam annehi sokehi. ","ja485:3.1":"Tinamiva vanamiva milayami, ","ja485:3.2":"Nadi aparipunnava sussami; ","ja485:3.3":"Tava candiya socantiya, ","ja485:3.4":"Na nam annehi sokehi. ","ja485:4.1":"Vassamiva sare pade, ","ja485:4.2":"Imani assuni vattare mayham; ","ja485:4.3":"Tava candiya socantiya, ","ja485:4.4":"Na nam annehi sokehi”. ","ja485:5.1":"“Papo khosi rajaputta, ","ja485:5.2":"Yo me icchitam patim varakiya; ","ja485:5.3":"Vijjhasi vanamulasmim, ","ja485:5.4":"Soyam viddho chama seti. ","ja485:6.1":"Imam mayham hadayasokam, ","ja485:6.2":"Patimuncatu rajaputta tava mata; ","ja485:6.3":"Yo mayham hadayasoko, ","ja485:6.4":"Kimpurisam avekkhamanaya. ","ja485:7.1":"Imam mayham hadayasokam, ","ja485:7.2":"Patimuncatu rajaputta tava jaya; ","ja485:7.3":"Yo mayham hadayasoko, ","ja485:7.4":"Kimpurisam avekkhamanaya. ","ja485:8.1":"Ma ca puttam ma ca patim, ","ja485:8.2":"Addakkhi rajaputta tava mata; ","ja485:8.3":"Yo kimpurisam avadhi, ","ja485:8.4":"Adusakam mayha kama hi. ","ja485:9.1":"Ma ca puttam ma ca patim, ","ja485:9.2":"Addakkhi rajaputta tava jaya; ","ja485:9.3":"Yo kimpurisam avadhi, ","ja485:9.4":"Adusakam mayha kama hi”. ","ja485:10.1":"“Ma tvam cande rodi, ","ja485:10.2":"Ma soci vanatimiramattakkhi; ","ja485:10.3":"Mama tvam hehisi bhariya, ","ja485:10.4":"Rajakule pujita naribhi”. ","ja485:11.1":"“Api nunaham marissam, ","ja485:11.2":"Naham rajaputta tava hessam; ","ja485:11.3":"Yo kimpurisam avadhi, ","ja485:11.4":"Adusakam mayha kama hi”. ","ja485:12.1":"“Api bhiruke api jivitukamike, ","ja485:12.2":"Kimpurisi gaccha himavantam; ","ja485:12.3":"Talisatagarabhojana, ","ja485:12.4":"Anne tam miga ramissanti”. ","ja485:13.1":"“Te pabbata ta ca kandara, ","ja485:13.2":"Ta ca giriguhayo tatheva titthanti; ","ja485:13.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:13.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:14.1":"Te pannasanthata ramaniya, ","ja485:14.2":"Valamigehi anucinna; ","ja485:14.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:14.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:15.1":"Te pupphasanthata ramaniya, ","ja485:15.2":"Valamigehi anucinna; ","ja485:15.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:15.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:16.1":"Accha savanti girivananadiyo, ","ja485:16.2":"Kusumabhikinnasotayo; ","ja485:16.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:16.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:17.1":"Nilani himavato pabbatassa, ","ja485:17.2":"Kutani dassaniyani; ","ja485:17.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:17.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:18.1":"Pitani himavato pabbatassa, ","ja485:18.2":"Kutani dassaniyani; ","ja485:18.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:18.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:19.1":"Tambani himavato pabbatassa, ","ja485:19.2":"Kutani dassaniyani; ","ja485:19.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:19.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:20.1":"Tungani himavato pabbatassa, ","ja485:20.2":"Kutani dassaniyani; ","ja485:20.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:20.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:21.1":"Setani himavato pabbatassa, ","ja485:21.2":"Kutani dassaniyani; ","ja485:21.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:21.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:22.1":"Citrani himavato pabbatassa, ","ja485:22.2":"Kutani dassaniyani; ","ja485:22.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:22.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:23.1":"Yakkhaganasevite gandhamadane, ","ja485:23.2":"Osadhebhi sanchanne; ","ja485:23.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:23.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam. ","ja485:24.1":"Kimpurisasevite gandhamadane, ","ja485:24.2":"Osadhebhi sanchanne; ","ja485:24.3":"Tattheva tam apassanti, ","ja485:24.4":"Kimpurisa katham aham kassam”. ","ja485:25.1":"“Vande te ayirabrahme, ","ja485:25.2":"Yo me icchitam patim varakiya; ","ja485:25.3":"Amatena abhisinci, ","ja485:25.4":"Samagatasmi piyatamena. ","ja485:26.1":"Vicarama dani girivana nadiyo, ","ja485:26.2":"Kusumabhikinnasotayo; ","ja485:26.3":"Nanadumavasanayo, ","ja485:26.4":"Piyamvada annamannassa”ti. ","ja485:27.1":"Candakinnarijatakam dutiyam. "}